description:
Life Springs Upwards: always twisting, blooming, spiking and twirling towards the light.

From Heather to Sakura. Life and the beauty of nature Prevail.

An abstract exploration of the explosion of plants in spring.

Best viewed as a high res version, as the work is very detailed.

S to save in current resolution

H to switch resolution, 2K>4K>6K>8K>10K width

G to toggle paper grain
name: Spring
